        "created_at": "2021-04-01T13:41:49.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"5\" data-topic=\"169655\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Thanks Don. Skipped this one, but did pick up some Chevali\u00e8res. Also have a bunch of 2019 on the way later this year!</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>You\u2019re in for a treat with everything you\u2019ve bought.</p>\n<p>IIRC I described this estate as Meursault\u2019s best-kept secret in TWA, and I\u2019d definitely stand by that. Though judging by social media, the secret is less and less well kept\u2026</p>",
