        "created_at": "2021-04-01T14:02:04.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"7\" data-topic=\"169655\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>You\u2019re in for a treat with everything you\u2019ve bought.</p>\n<p>IIRC I described this estate as Meursault\u2019s best-kept secret in TWA, and I\u2019d definitely stand by that. Though judging by social media, the secret is less and less well kept\u2026</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Around here, the pricing has also escaped from the \u201csecret well kept\u201d bracket! It\u2019s now slightly more expensive than Boillot.</p>",
